content:
I'd be happy to help you keep track of your workout schedule. However, I'm a large language model, I don't have the capability to set reminders or store personal data. But I can help you create a schedule that you can use to keep track of your workouts.

Here's a suggested schedule for your triathlon clinic and swim lessons:

**Weekly Schedule:**

* Saturday: Triathlon Clinic
* Tuesday: Swim Lessons (morning)
* Thursday: Swim Lessons (morning)

You can copy and paste this into a digital calendar or planner, or write it down in a physical planner. Make sure to set reminders for each event so you don't forget!

If you need help with anything else, such as planning your workouts or creating a training plan, feel free to ask and I'll do my best to assist you.
